Package: rkal
Type: Package
Title: Run, Import, and Export 'kallisto' Quantifications
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Pickering", email="alexvpickering@gmail.com",
                role=c("cre", "aut"),
                comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0002-6759"))
Description: Interface to 'kallisto' pseudo quantification utility. 'rkal' 
    automates running, importing, and exporting  'kallisto' quantification. 
    This includes importing samples from ARCHS4 HDF5 data objects. Though 
    general, 'rkal' is primarly intended for use by other packages e.g. 
    `crossmeta` for differential expression and meta analyses.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
SystemRequirements: kallisto
